latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We are back on our mission to help the needy !

Day 2 supplies: 
200 food packets
75 water bottles
Clothes for the kids , men and women.
Essentials for women .
And snacks for the kids.

The aftermath of day 1 left us all numb ! Looking at the situation at hand, our will and determination to help these people, grew stronger .
The scenes in the city remained the same as day 1 , things got out of hand when people lost their belongings. Yes all of it !

After putting out the footage of day1 , a few more people decided to join us and volunteered along with us. The media too joined in.

Thank you all for your support and contributions! 
 
We are preparing ourselves for the next leg of the mission ! Stay tuned ......
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: MISSION HUMANITY  HYDERABAD RESCUE DAY- 1  FLOODS  HEAVY RAINS
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In this human world, the misery of the less fortunate can only be lifted by a kind and compassionate heart!

We may be comfortable living in our home, We may not be affected by hunger during this time of crisis. The turmoil caused by the pandemic and the floods have caused havoc in the lives of our dear city dwellers. It's time for us all to do out bit.
And this is what we had done for the needy today!
We started our day by preparing food for 150 people (including 120 footi tetra packs for the kids).

We tried contacting people to help us out with the areas that had been badly affected by the recent rains. Hashim Nagar a locality near Charminar was one of them.

We walked towards the locality and all we could see is chaos. The entire locality was half underwater and people on their roofs.
The condition of the people and kids is deteriorating since they have not eaten for 48 hours. No water to drink and no electricity!

We have seen the worse .!!

This footage can speak for itself.

NOTE: For any contributions or people who are willing to volunteer contact 9703296543 (Gpay/Phone pe/ Paytm). 
.
.
.
